I"v<p>An overview of my publications is accessible via <a href="https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=6DhK95QAAAAJ&amp;hl=en">Google Scholar</a>. Some additional items, such as posters presented at conferences, are available from <a href="https://www.researchgate.net/profile/Francesco-Lombardi-5/research">ResearchGate</a>.</p>

